  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0da7 \u0d87\u0db4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bail for Cyril Vasant",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Chief Magistrate Nandana Amarasinghe today (29) ordered the release of Cyril Wasantha, a social activist who was remanded in custody in connection with the alleged forced entry into the television corporation, on two sureties of Rs 25,000 cash and Rs 5 lakh each. .",
        "The Kurunduwatta Police also submitted to the court that the investigation regarding the first suspect in this incident, Mr. Dhanish Ali, has not yet been completed.",
        "Taking into consideration the facts presented, the Magistrate ordered the Kurunduwatta Police to report the progress regarding the incident on September 26."
      ],
